The "Alma mater" infobox entry shows "{{tq|[[Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania|Wharton School]] ([[Bachelor of Science|BS]]{{thinsp}}[[Economics|Econ.]])}}", does not mention [[Fordham University]]. ([[Talk:Donald Trump/Archive 56#Universities in infobox|April 2017]], [[Talk:Donald Trump/Archive 58#Reopening discussion about 'Universities in infobox'|April 2017]], [[Talk:Donald Trump/Archive 122#University name in the Infobox?|Aug 2020]], [[Talk:Donald Trump/Archive 129#Survey: University degree in infobox|Dec 2020]])
