'''33.''' {{anchor|C33}} Do not mention [[Barack Obama citizenship conspiracy theories|"birtherism"]] in the lead section. ([[Talk:Donald Trump/Archive 93#RfC: Birtherism in the lede|RfC Nov 2018]])

