Supersedes [[#C7|#7]]. Include in the lead: {{tq|Trump has made many false or misleading statements during his campaign and presidency. The statements have been documented by [[fact-checker]]s, and the media have widely described the phenomenon as unprecedented in American politics.}} ([[Talk:Donald Trump/Archive 95#RfC: Should the lead be updated to reflect that Trump has continued to make false or misleading statements throughout his campaign and presidency?|RfC Feb 2019]])
}}

