#Close the thread using {{tlx|archive top}} and {{tlx|archive bottom}}, referring to this consensus item. Suggested closure for copy-and-paste:<br><code><nowiki>{{atop|Please read [[WP:TRUMPRCB]]. Closing per [[Talk:Donald Trump#C61|consensus 61]]. Eligible for manual archival after this time tomorrow. ~~~~}}</nowiki></code><br>[existing thread]<br><code><nowiki>{{abot}}</nowiki></code>
